@76="Polymorph Self
(Alteration)

Level: 4
Range: 0
Duration: 1 turn + 3 rounds/level
Casting Time: 4
Area of Effect: The caster
Saving Throw: None

When this spell is cast, the wizard is able to assume the form of several creatures creature. For the duration of the spell, the caster can transform into any of the new forms at any time and as many times as <PRO_HESHE> wishes. The caster gains the natural attacks of the new form in some cases and may use weapons in others. The mental attributes of the wizard remain the same, but all physical attributes are obtained from the new form. Also, any natural protections that the new form offers are conferred to the wizard, such as the resistance to missile and crushing weapons possessed by the slime form.

The possible forms given by Polymorph Self are:
- Hill Giant Barbarian: can cause massive damage; barbarian rage protects against many attacks
- Ogre Mage: can make powerful slashing attacks; this is the only form in which the wizard can cast spells
- Mustard Jelly: capable of poisoning or slowing opponents 
- Spider: can poison an opponent or trap them in webs
- Hell Hound: immune to fire, and can breathe fire on an opponent
- Rat: difficult to hit; can move stealthily"

